title: Godsmack - April 26 2015 - Jacksonville, Florida
description:
Godsmack
7:30 PM
Sunday, April 26, 2015
Rockville Festival - Jack Daniel's Stage
Jacksonville, Florida, USA


Band Lineup:

Sully Erna (Lead Vocals, Rhythm Guitar, Keyboard, Harmonica, Drums, Percussion)

Recording Comments:

Good concert, the recording came out well, the only thing of mention is that the recording isn't extremely loud due to the huge gap in between the fans and the stage (which Sully Erna mentions on track 03). I was up front to the right.


Recording 'Proof' Comments:

On track 03, "1000hp" at 4:03-4:06, Sully Erna says, "Well what's up Jacksonville, motherfuckin' Florida?!". The rest of the recording has other mentions as well.
